      "description": "Agent-native CLI architect for GUI software — 7-phase SOP to wrap any GUI app into a stateful, agent-usable CLI with REPL + subcommand modes, backend integration, test planning, and SKILL.md generation; based on HKUDS/CLI-Anything (Mar 2026, 34k+ stars)"
