      "section": "Coding & Development",
      "description": "Whole-repo structural audit — nine-dimension debt sweep (architectural decay, consistency rot, type debt, test debt, dependency rot, performance hygiene, observability, security hygiene, documentation drift); forced orientation before judgment, mandatory `file:line` citations, required \"looks bad but is actually fine\" section; based on ksimback/tech-debt-skill (Apr 2026)"
