      "description": "Designer prompt for Anthropic's Claude Code sub-agents — when to use sub-agent vs skill vs inline, kebab-case naming, routing description authoring, least-privilege tool allowlists, isolated context discipline, output-contract lock-in, routing stress test; based on Anthropic's Claude Code Sub-Agents docs (Feb 2026) and wshobson/agents + VoltAgent/awesome-claude-code-subagents (2026)"
