      "description": "Multi-book binding ruleset for AI coding agents — Clean Code (readability, naming, functions, side effects), Clean Architecture (dependency direction, boundaries, adapters), Domain-Driven Design (bounded contexts, aggregates, ubiquitous language), Designing Data-Intensive Applications (consistency, durability, replication, schema evolution); unified review checklist; based on ciembor/agent-rules-books (Apr 2026, 1.4k+ stars)"
