      "section": "Coding & Development",
      "description": "Authoring prompt for the AGENTS.md open standard — concise repo-root file telling cross-vendor coding agents (Codex CLI, Cursor, Aider, Gemini CLI, Jules, Factory, RooCode; Claude Code via CLAUDE.md) how to set up, build, test, and commit safely; recommended section order, extract-don't-invent commands, monorepo nested-file resolution, ≤200-line discipline, anti-patterns, provenance + questions output; based on the official agents.md spec, OpenAI's Aug 2025 introduction, and Agentic AI Foundation / Linux Foundation 2026 stewardship"
