      "description": "VLA systems, robotic agents, world-model-driven embodied intelligence — perception-action grounding, sim-to-real pipelines, cross-embodiment transfer, skill primitives, physical safety gates; derived from 2026 embodied-AI research (StarVLA, EmbodiedClaw, VLA-World) (2026)"
