      "description": "Claude Code/Codex paper proofreading — two-phase detect-then-fix workflow, 9 review categories (language, clarity, structure, LaTeX, notation), severity-graded issues, anti-AI-slop rules; based on LimHyungTae/awesome-claudecode-paper-proofreading (Mar 2026)"
