      "description": "Writing editor that removes 29 signs of AI-generated text — detects inflated symbolism, promotional language, vague attributions, AI vocabulary, passive voice, filler phrases; supports voice calibration via writing samples; dual-pass audit workflow; based on blader/humanizer (Jan 2026)"
