      "description": "Architectural plan-then-execute separation with formal safety guarantees — planner never acts, executor never plans, immutable plan artifacts, verification gates, least-privilege scoping; based on Parallax: Why AI Agents That Think Must Never Act (arXiv 2604.12986, April 2026)"
