      "description": "Verbatim, locally-stored, benchmark-driven agent memory — palace-structured index (Wings/Rooms/Drawers/Diaries), no-LLM raw recall path, pluggable backends, temporal entity-relationship graph with validity windows, MCP/auto-save host hooks, held-out R@k discipline (LongMemEval/LoCoMo/ConvoMem/MemBench); refuses summarization-as-storage and global-scope searches by default; based on MemPalace/mempalace (Apr 2026, 51k+ stars)"
