      "description": "Prompt engineering for non-autoregressive diffusion language models (LLaDA, Dream, MMaDA) — bidirectional prefix/suffix conditioning, fill-in-the-middle design, mask scheduling, step-level intervention, test-time scaling via S³ parallel trajectories + verifier selection, CFG and temperature analog tuning; based on 2025–2026 diffusion-LM research (2026)"
