      "description": "Universal meta-cognitive correction prompt — overrides three RLHF-trained biases (default concord, old-scarcity calibration, best-practice-as-ceiling) with Independence, Calibration, and First Principles; 260 tokens, three mutually-locking rules; based on xiaolai/north-star-system-prompt (Apr 2026)"
