      "description": "Full game-dev studio orchestration — 3-tier agent hierarchy (Directors/Leads/Specialists), engine-specific specialist sets, vertical delegation + horizontal consultation, change propagation, path-scoped coding rules, automated safety hooks, and slash-command team orchestration; based on Donchitos/Claude-Code-Game-Studios (Feb 2026, 19k+ stars)"
